1
00:00:04,980 --> 00:00:09,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mizuho's not the only one that's 
been looking your way, Kizuki.</font>

2
00:00:09,850 --> 00:00:11,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I love you, Kizuki.</font>

3
00:00:15,830 --> 00:00:18,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't go out with you, Airu.</font>

4
00:00:18,650 --> 00:00:20,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because I love Mizuho.</font>

5
00:00:22,100 --> 00:00:23,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

6
00:00:23,730 --> 00:00:25,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're someone who's 
very important to me, Airu.</font>

7
00:00:26,510 --> 00:00:29,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to keep going to school 
with you tomorrow.</font>

8
00:00:30,180 --> 00:00:32,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And talk about a bunch of things 
and laugh with you.</font>

9
00:00:33,660 --> 00:00:34,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

10
00:00:36,560 --> 00:00:40,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="30">2030</font></font>

11
00:00:50,860 --> 00:00:54,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll take a raw sea urchin pasta 
and the gnocchi with gorgonzola sauce.</font>

12
00:00:57,200 --> 00:01:00,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who makes an order instead 
of a normal greeting?</font>

13
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:03,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Also, I'm still prepping.</font>

14
00:01:03,270 --> 00:01:04,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know.</font>

15
00:01:06,360 --> 00:01:07,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was just kidding.</font>

16
00:01:12,270 --> 00:01:14,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This place looks like it's doing well.</font>

17
00:01:14,710 --> 00:01:16,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course it is.</font>

18
00:01:16,720 --> 00:01:19,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm a master chef.</font>

19
00:01:21,960 --> 00:01:23,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A master at cooking, sure.</font>

20
00:01:23,840 --> 00:01:25,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But what about your personal life?</font>

21
00:01:27,540 --> 00:01:29,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I heard Kizuki's back.</font>

22
00:01:30,700 --> 00:01:32,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So? What are you going to do?</font>

23
00:01:32,940 --> 00:01:34,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you mean?</font>

24
00:01:35,570 --> 00:01:39,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I guess you've always 
put your friends first.</font>

25
00:01:40,140 --> 00:01:41,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm the third lead.</font>

26
00:01:41,890 --> 00:01:44,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Therefore, I'll get to 
take everything in the end.</font>

27
00:01:44,810 --> 00:01:46,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What did you say?</font>

28
00:01:50,960 --> 00:01:53,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're hungry, right?</font>

29
00:01:54,510 --> 00:01:56,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Eat this.</font>

30
00:03:27,020 --> 00:03:30,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="30">2020</font></font>

31
00:03:32,450 --> 00:03:33,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mi-chan.</font>

32
00:03:35,650 --> 00:03:37,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mi-chan.</font>

33
00:03:37,260 --> 00:03:40,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, you're in your room.</font>

34
00:03:40,220 --> 00:03:41,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why didn't you answer?</font>

35
00:03:45,040 --> 00:03:49,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This year's New Year's Eve party 
will be at Izumi-san's house.</font>

36
00:03:52,360 --> 00:03:53,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you listening?</font>

37
00:03:54,140 --> 00:03:55,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh-huh.</font>

38
00:03:57,060 --> 00:04:00,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I noticed that the boys 
aren't over today either.</font>

39
00:04:00,360 --> 00:04:01,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's rare.</font>

40
00:04:01,910 --> 00:04:04,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is it because you'll all be 
busy applying to universities next year?</font>

41
00:04:04,120 --> 00:04:06,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe they started studying.</font>

42
00:04:07,430 --> 00:04:09,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry to bother you.</font>

43
00:04:14,630 --> 00:04:18,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'll accept everything.</i></font>

44
00:04:19,770 --> 00:04:24,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This is the outcome</i></font>

45
00:04:24,830 --> 00:04:27,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="20"><font color="#565451"><b><font face="Times New Roman">{\an7}Every Score Shall Absolutely Improve!</font></b></font></font></font>

46
00:04:24,830 --> 00:04:27,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="10"><font color="#7989cc"><b><font face="Times New Roman">Determination and <font color="#d77e67">Effort</font></font></b></font></font></font>

47
00:04:28,500 --> 00:04:29,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>of the decisions I made.</i></font>

48
00:04:34,000 --> 00:04:37,590
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#2e3744">{\an8}Izumi</font>

49
00:04:34,610 --> 00:04:36,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hello, everyone.</font>

50
00:04:36,350 --> 00:04:37,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a busy time of year.</font>

51
00:04:37,590 --> 00:04:41,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I'm glad you could join us here
 at the humble Izumi residence</font>

52
00:04:41,140 --> 00:04:42,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to celebrate the New Year.</font>

53
00:04:42,710 --> 00:04:44,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's only a few hours 
left of this year—</font>

54
00:04:44,160 --> 00:04:45,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're taking too long!</font>

55
00:04:45,650 --> 00:04:46,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cheers!</font>

56
00:04:46,970 --> 00:04:48,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cheers!</font>

57
00:04:51,170 --> 00:04:53,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You get drunk way too fast, Nishino-san!</font>

58
00:04:55,120 --> 00:04:58,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I always make Mizuho feel sad...</font>

59
00:04:58,380 --> 00:05:00,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And she seems to have 
a lot on her mind lately...</font>

60
00:05:00,670 --> 00:05:03,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She didn't even come 
to tonight's party...</font>

61
00:05:08,270 --> 00:05:11,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm just so worried for my girl...</font>

62
00:05:11,240 --> 00:05:13,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, come on. She's at that age.</font>

63
00:05:13,940 --> 00:05:15,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure there's just 
a lot going on in her life.</font>

64
00:05:15,380 --> 00:05:16,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's right.</font>

65
00:05:16,760 --> 00:05:17,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh-huh.</font>

66
00:05:17,870 --> 00:05:19,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just leave her be.</font>

67
00:05:20,030 --> 00:05:22,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mizuho-chan's going to be all right.</font>

68
00:05:22,470 --> 00:05:24,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you really think so?</font>

69
00:05:24,640 --> 00:05:27,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We can only shut up, trust, 
and watch over them.</font>

70
00:05:28,040 --> 00:05:32,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But in my case, if my kid 
needed me, that's when...</font>

71
00:05:33,220 --> 00:05:35,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll give it my all to protect them,</font>

72
00:05:35,260 --> 00:05:38,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">even if it means making 
an enemy of the whole world.</font>

73
00:05:39,680 --> 00:05:41,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Izumi-san, you're so cool!</font>

74
00:05:41,520 --> 00:05:43,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You really are!</font>

75
00:05:44,830 --> 00:05:46,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay then, cheers!</font>

76
00:05:46,710 --> 00:05:48,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cheers!</font>

77
00:05:48,490 --> 00:05:49,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you so much.</font>

78
00:05:49,970 --> 00:05:51,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Happy New Year!</font>

79
00:05:51,230 --> 00:05:53,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Happy New Year to you, too!</font>

80
00:05:56,260 --> 00:05:57,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ugh.</font>

81
00:05:57,880 --> 00:05:59,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's down already.</font>

82
00:05:59,820 --> 00:06:01,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So useless.</font>

83
00:06:01,340 --> 00:06:03,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dad's definitely gonna be hung over.</font>

84
00:06:06,130 --> 00:06:07,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's this?</font>

85
00:06:07,180 --> 00:06:13,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font color="#f598ed">Blam!</font></b></font>

86
00:06:07,180 --> 00:06:13,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font color="#e6ae4a">Good Vibes!</font></b></font>

87
00:06:07,450 --> 00:06:10,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A pic from when I was in high school.</font>

88
00:06:10,960 --> 00:06:12,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're so young here!</font>

89
00:06:13,510 --> 00:06:15,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're even more flashy than I am!</font>

90
00:06:15,090 --> 00:06:17,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cute, right?</font>

91
00:06:22,330 --> 00:06:24,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you get your tan from the beach?</font>

92
00:06:24,210 --> 00:06:25,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At a tanning salon.</font>

93
00:06:25,400 --> 00:06:27,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I tanned nicely, right?</font>

94
00:06:27,110 --> 00:06:28,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seriously?</font>

95
00:06:28,330 --> 00:06:30,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everyone said they wanted to see it.</font>

96
00:06:30,520 --> 00:06:31,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I brought it out.</font>

97
00:06:31,700 --> 00:06:32,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mom.</font>

98
00:06:38,130 --> 00:06:39,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's up?</font>

99
00:06:40,100 --> 00:06:42,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I... confessed...</font>

100
00:06:44,410 --> 00:06:47,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To Kizuki. On Christmas.</font>

101
00:06:49,460 --> 00:06:52,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And he rejected me.</font>

102
00:06:53,350 --> 00:06:57,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Back in middle school. 
That's why I ran away from home.</font>

103
00:07:00,610 --> 00:07:03,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry I couldn't tell you 
this whole time.</font>

104
00:07:03,330 --> 00:07:04,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't apologize.</font>

105
00:07:06,240 --> 00:07:08,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It doesn't matter.</font>

106
00:07:10,870 --> 00:07:13,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whether you're a delinquent, 
or ran away from home,</font>

107
00:07:13,730 --> 00:07:15,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">or who you fall in love with...</font>

108
00:07:16,320 --> 00:07:20,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Since the day you were born, 
you're my irreplaceable son.</font>

109
00:07:25,180 --> 00:07:28,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry you had to bottle all of this up 
on your own this whole time.</font>

110
00:07:28,970 --> 00:07:31,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you for telling me...</font>

111
00:07:32,380 --> 00:07:34,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure you gave it your all to confess.</font>

112
00:07:46,730 --> 00:07:49,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Want some hot cocoa?</font>

113
00:07:51,760 --> 00:07:52,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

114
00:07:55,750 --> 00:07:58,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an2}<font size="34"><font face="Arial"><b><font color="#93b1bf">Wanna do something for the first sunrise?</font></b></font></font></font>

115
00:08:25,250 --> 00:08:27,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A Christmas present?</font>

116
00:08:28,370 --> 00:08:30,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I didn't give you mine yet, right?</i></font>

117
00:08:31,160 --> 00:08:33,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come to Koigahama Beach right now.</font>

118
00:08:33,220 --> 00:08:35,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What? Right now?</i></font>

119
00:08:35,440 --> 00:08:37,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't even go to the Christmas party.</font>

120
00:08:37,960 --> 00:08:40,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't accept a gift...</font>

121
00:08:40,010 --> 00:08:42,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Are we just not even going to 
see each other anymore?</i></font>

122
00:08:43,890 --> 00:08:46,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Is this what our relationship amounts to?</i></font>

123
00:08:47,090 --> 00:08:50,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Remember when you moved to Koigahama?</font>

124
00:08:50,550 --> 00:08:54,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You and I were the first to meet 
before anyone else.</font>

125
00:08:54,350 --> 00:08:56,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And then we met the others.</font>

126
00:08:56,270 --> 00:08:58,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'd play until we forgot 
what time it was.</font>

127
00:08:58,920 --> 00:09:01,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'd fight and make up.</font>

128
00:09:01,240 --> 00:09:04,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">During summer break, 
Christmas, and even New Year's.</font>

129
00:09:05,270 --> 00:09:08,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No matter when and where, 
we brought chaos together.</font>

130
00:09:08,950 --> 00:09:15,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So now that you and Kizuki are going out, 
you're going to reset our history?</font>

131
00:09:16,050 --> 00:09:17,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Just like that?</i></font>

132
00:09:17,540 --> 00:09:19,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's not like us at all.</i></font>

133
00:09:33,970 --> 00:09:35,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">C'mon, Airu.</font>

134
00:09:35,510 --> 00:09:36,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah! Stop that!</font>

135
00:09:36,860 --> 00:09:39,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your hands are cold!</font>

136
00:09:39,540 --> 00:09:40,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Help me, Shin-chan!</font>

137
00:09:40,750 --> 00:09:41,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't come near me.</font>

138
00:09:42,850 --> 00:09:44,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're late.</font>

139
00:09:53,090 --> 00:09:54,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I called them, too.</font>

140
00:09:55,270 --> 00:09:58,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is your Christmas present.</font>

141
00:09:58,700 --> 00:10:00,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So don't you dare say you don't want it.</font>

142
00:10:01,210 --> 00:10:02,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Syugo!</font>

143
00:10:02,950 --> 00:10:06,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Syugo barged into my room 
and forced me out of bed.</font>

144
00:10:06,630 --> 00:10:08,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was studying when he suddenly came in...</font>

145
00:10:10,450 --> 00:10:12,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You better be grateful for me!</font>

146
00:10:12,670 --> 00:10:15,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We are! Really!</font>

147
00:10:19,650 --> 00:10:21,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Guys, it's been too long!</font>

148
00:10:21,340 --> 00:10:23,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This feels a little surreal.</font>

149
00:10:25,650 --> 00:10:26,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We...</i></font>

150
00:10:29,760 --> 00:10:30,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh!</font>

151
00:10:33,850 --> 00:10:35,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>...are changing</i></font>

152
00:10:39,070 --> 00:10:41,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>in every waking moment.</i></font>

153
00:10:41,660 --> 00:10:43,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoa!</font>

154
00:10:43,840 --> 00:10:46,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No one can stop us from changing.</i></font>

155
00:10:46,540 --> 00:10:48,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We can't go back either.</i></font>

156
00:10:50,200 --> 00:10:51,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But...</i></font>

157
00:10:54,280 --> 00:10:57,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We've moved forward, huh?</font>

158
00:11:02,270 --> 00:11:03,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yup.</font>

159
00:11:05,940 --> 00:11:07,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you, Syugo.</font>

160
00:11:09,920 --> 00:11:12,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is the best Christmas present.</font>

161
00:11:13,710 --> 00:11:15,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">R-Right?</font>

162
00:11:15,280 --> 00:11:17,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Though it's the new year now.</font>

163
00:11:18,090 --> 00:11:19,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks, Syugo.</font>

164
00:11:20,360 --> 00:11:23,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so happy that I got to see 
the first sunrise with you guys again!</font>

165
00:11:25,330 --> 00:11:27,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's not your line to say!</font>

166
00:11:28,510 --> 00:11:31,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're the one to blame, Kizuki!</font>

167
00:11:31,670 --> 00:11:34,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You messed up our Christmas party!</font>

168
00:11:34,950 --> 00:11:36,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take responsibility and go for a swim!</font>

169
00:11:36,890 --> 00:11:37,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

170
00:11:38,610 --> 00:11:39,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A long time ago...</font>

171
00:11:40,410 --> 00:11:45,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You were on your high-horse and told me 
to "go get what you want to get."</font>

172
00:11:47,330 --> 00:11:49,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You fit the "honor student" role better.</font>

173
00:11:51,090 --> 00:11:53,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shin, I've told you before.</font>

174
00:11:54,900 --> 00:12:00,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The one that gets it all 
in the end is the "third lead."</font>

175
00:12:00,720 --> 00:12:05,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can keep being the "honor student" 
for the rest of your life.</font>

176
00:12:05,950 --> 00:12:06,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?!</font>

177
00:12:17,850 --> 00:12:19,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wanna go visit the shrine 
while we're at it?</font>

178
00:12:19,620 --> 00:12:20,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wanna go!</font>

179
00:12:21,570 --> 00:12:25,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh wait, I'm still in my pajamas.</font>

180
00:12:25,440 --> 00:12:26,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sheesh.</font>

181
00:12:28,270 --> 00:12:30,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go get dressed, Kizuki!</font>

182
00:12:50,760 --> 00:12:53,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We're moving forward. Together.</i></font>

183
00:12:56,050 --> 00:12:57,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Later!</font>

184
00:12:57,300 --> 00:12:58,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bye-bye!</font>

185
00:12:59,620 --> 00:13:01,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey you!</font>

186
00:13:01,050 --> 00:13:02,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where's Hazawa-senpai?</font>

187
00:13:02,890 --> 00:13:05,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't see him in the classroom.</font>

188
00:13:06,180 --> 00:13:07,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe he's at swim club?</font>

189
00:13:07,560 --> 00:13:10,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to be blessed 
by his face before I leave.</font>

190
00:13:10,180 --> 00:13:11,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's check out the pool then!</font>

191
00:13:13,140 --> 00:13:15,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Kizuki's popular as always.</i></font>

192
00:13:16,230 --> 00:13:19,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And sometimes that pains me.</i></font>

193
00:13:30,820 --> 00:13:31,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kizuki!</font>

194
00:13:32,340 --> 00:13:34,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you trying to go home without me?</font>

195
00:13:34,710 --> 00:13:36,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">W-Well, I...</font>

196
00:13:38,730 --> 00:13:40,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After all, we're a couple now.</font>

197
00:13:45,930 --> 00:13:47,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go home together.</font>

198
00:13:47,910 --> 00:13:49,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Kizuki's my boyfriend and...</i></font>

199
00:13:50,290 --> 00:13:52,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm his girlfriend.</i></font>

200
00:13:55,610 --> 00:13:56,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But...</i></font>

201
00:14:00,360 --> 00:14:02,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Why can't I be more honest about this?</i></font>

202
00:14:07,120 --> 00:14:11,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How could I be such a sinful guy?</font>

203
00:14:11,810 --> 00:14:16,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To think that I'd get these from 
Kasumi-senpai and Fuka-senpai this year...</font>

204
00:14:17,980 --> 00:14:21,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My popularity is unstoppable 
with the older ladies.</font>

205
00:14:21,030 --> 00:14:22,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you talking about?</font>

206
00:14:22,290 --> 00:14:23,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're boxes of love.</font>

207
00:14:23,920 --> 00:14:24,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Say what?</font>

208
00:14:25,590 --> 00:14:32,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I felt bad receiving Valentines 
every year, so I planned this.</font>

209
00:14:32,100 --> 00:14:35,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font size="16"><font color="#ab4b48">Karaoke Chocolate
Trading Party</font></font></font>

210
00:14:32,100 --> 00:14:35,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="20"><font face="Arial"><font color="#e29aa2">RSVP</font></font></font></font>

211
00:14:32,390 --> 00:14:35,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A karaoke chocolate trading party!</font>

212
00:14:36,240 --> 00:14:39,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A-As expected of a social butterfly...</font>

213
00:14:40,010 --> 00:14:41,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">By the way, where's Shin-chan?</font>

214
00:14:41,620 --> 00:14:43,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He was headed to cram school.</font>

215
00:14:43,770 --> 00:14:46,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So he ran away from us.</font>

216
00:14:46,030 --> 00:14:47,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yup.</font>

217
00:14:47,460 --> 00:14:49,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, Kashiwagi-kun...</font>

218
00:14:49,870 --> 00:14:51,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't want it.</font>

219
00:14:51,390 --> 00:14:53,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I haven't said anything yet!</font>

220
00:14:53,250 --> 00:14:54,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just leave it.</font>

221
00:14:54,870 --> 00:14:57,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>His "don't speak to me" aura 
is off the charts...</i></font>

222
00:14:59,290 --> 00:15:01,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In that case, let's head home.</font>

223
00:15:01,280 --> 00:15:02,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, Mizuho.</font>

224
00:15:02,850 --> 00:15:07,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just so you know, you're not getting my 
special homemade chocolates this year.</font>

225
00:15:07,530 --> 00:15:09,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Why not?</font>

226
00:15:10,770 --> 00:15:13,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like I can give it to someone 
with a boyfriend!</font>

227
00:15:14,730 --> 00:15:16,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">See you two later!</font>

228
00:15:17,820 --> 00:15:19,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, yeah...</font>

229
00:15:26,000 --> 00:15:29,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Valentine's Day... 
I haven't planned anything.</i></font>

230
00:15:31,120 --> 00:15:33,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's nippy, but feels good out.</font>

231
00:15:35,090 --> 00:15:37,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I panicked and bought some chocolates...</i></font>

232
00:15:39,190 --> 00:15:41,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But just how do I give it to him? 
What do I say?</i></font>

233
00:15:52,620 --> 00:15:56,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was thinking how amazing it is 
that I get to keep you all to myself.</font>

234
00:16:01,810 --> 00:16:04,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, sorry.</font>

235
00:16:05,270 --> 00:16:08,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I... I'm still not used to this.</font>

236
00:16:10,200 --> 00:16:11,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">L-Let's go home.</font>

237
00:16:20,240 --> 00:16:22,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm a certified clown for sure.</i></font>

238
00:16:23,770 --> 00:16:25,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's no good...</i></font>

239
00:16:25,040 --> 00:16:27,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm not fit for romance.</i></font>

240
00:16:29,970 --> 00:16:34,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If this persists, I'll never change.</i></font>

241
00:16:39,730 --> 00:16:42,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font color="#676d70">Kizuki</font></font>

242
00:16:39,980 --> 00:16:42,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font color="#8a8ed8">m 0 0 l 230 0 l 230 215 l 0 215</font></font>

243
00:16:39,980 --> 00:16:42,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an7}<font size="15"><font color="#3d3d48">Let's go
somewhere on Sunday!</font></font></font>

244
00:16:46,230 --> 00:16:50,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an7}<font size="19"><font color="#3d3d48">Turns out I'm going with the Southern Kanto Select Team for training camp. Starting tomorrow until the 16th.</font></font></font>

245
00:16:46,230 --> 00:16:50,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an7}<font size="19"><font color="#3d3d48">It's at the international swimming pool.</font></font></font>

246
00:16:52,320 --> 00:16:53,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Training camp?</font>

247
00:17:02,800 --> 00:17:05,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Those that finished 1000 can take a break!</font>

248
00:17:06,250 --> 00:17:10,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font color="#676d70">Mizuho</font></font>

249
00:17:06,250 --> 00:17:10,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an7}<font size="14"><font color="#3d3d48">I see, that's amazing! Gotcha!</font></font></font>

250
00:17:06,250 --> 00:17:10,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an7}<font size="14"><font color="#3d3d48">Good Luck!</font></font></font>

251
00:17:06,250 --> 00:17:10,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an7}<font size="17"><font color="#3d3d48">Yeah!</font></font></font>

252
00:17:13,760 --> 00:17:17,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font color="#85817f">He hasn't messaged me...</font></font>

253
00:17:22,930 --> 00:17:25,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Are you busy with practice?</i></font>

254
00:17:26,850 --> 00:17:32,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Why did I let go of 
Kizuki's hand back then?</i></font>

255
00:17:36,470 --> 00:17:38,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh! Thanks.</font>

256
00:17:38,790 --> 00:17:41,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was under the TV.</font>

257
00:17:41,200 --> 00:17:43,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I knew I must have 
dropped it at your place.</font>

258
00:17:44,700 --> 00:17:45,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm glad.</font>

259
00:17:47,230 --> 00:17:48,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong?</font>

260
00:17:48,610 --> 00:17:50,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You seem down.</font>

261
00:17:50,050 --> 00:17:51,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? Really?</font>

262
00:17:53,720 --> 00:17:55,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="18"><font color="#ebe4de"><font face="Arial">Kizuki</font></font></font></font>

263
00:17:53,720 --> 00:17:55,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="12"><font color="#ebe4de"><font face="Arial">Incoming Call...</font></font></font></font>

264
00:17:53,720 --> 00:17:55,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="12"><font color="#ebe4de"><font face="Arial">Slide to Answer</font></font></font></font>

265
00:17:56,050 --> 00:17:57,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Hey! Mizuho!</i></font>

266
00:17:59,850 --> 00:18:01,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kizuki! Guess what—</font>

267
00:18:01,730 --> 00:18:04,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Kizuki? Who are you talking to?</i></font>

268
00:18:04,700 --> 00:18:06,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Give it back, Taiyo!</i></font>

269
00:18:06,810 --> 00:18:10,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We have a meeting at 4:30, Kizuki.</i></font>

270
00:18:11,320 --> 00:18:12,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Hey, Mizuho—</i></font>

271
00:18:12,160 --> 00:18:13,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Gather around!</i></font>

272
00:18:14,120 --> 00:18:15,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Sorry. Maybe later, Mizuho.</i></font>

273
00:18:18,330 --> 00:18:19,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="22"><font color="#ebe4de"><font face="Arial">Call Ended</font></font></font></font>

274
00:18:19,660 --> 00:18:21,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Kizuki's world...</i></font>

275
00:18:22,330 --> 00:18:24,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>keeps expanding.</i></font>

276
00:18:24,770 --> 00:18:26,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No time to feel nervous.</font>

277
00:18:27,630 --> 00:18:31,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Knowing you, you must be 
thinking something dumb</font>

278
00:18:31,740 --> 00:18:33,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">like "Oh no, I'm no match for Kizuki..."</font>

279
00:18:34,830 --> 00:18:37,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're loved by the person you love.</font>

280
00:18:38,910 --> 00:18:41,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're in the best possible reality.</font>

281
00:18:41,910 --> 00:18:43,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you understand that?</font>

282
00:18:44,350 --> 00:18:47,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's a huge miracle.</font>

283
00:18:51,020 --> 00:18:52,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Airu...</font>

284
00:18:54,220 --> 00:18:55,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

285
00:18:59,200 --> 00:19:00,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Even if it's just for a second...</i></font>

286
00:19:02,500 --> 00:19:04,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}The next station is: Hiyoshi.</i></font>

287
00:19:04,720 --> 00:19:06,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}The doors on the right will open.</i></font>

288
00:19:07,210 --> 00:19:08,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I need to see Kizuki.</i></font>

289
00:19:11,120 --> 00:19:15,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And when I do, I'll tell him my feelings.</i></font>

290
00:19:24,990 --> 00:19:26,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This is it.</i></font>

291
00:19:29,660 --> 00:19:33,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I think it was at the Sub Arena.</i></font>

292
00:19:35,030 --> 00:19:36,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You there!</font>

293
00:19:37,550 --> 00:19:39,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you family with the athletes?</font>

294
00:19:39,410 --> 00:19:41,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Or a former player?</font>

295
00:19:41,030 --> 00:19:43,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, I'm not.</font>

296
00:19:43,260 --> 00:19:47,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can't enter without 
prior approval for entry.</font>

297
00:19:47,530 --> 00:19:48,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh.</font>

298
00:19:48,370 --> 00:19:53,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-Then could you please get this 
to Kizuki Hazawa for me?</font>

299
00:19:54,570 --> 00:19:56,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We get people like you 
a lot around this time.</font>

300
00:19:56,980 --> 00:19:59,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fans like you, bringing 
chocolates and such.</font>

301
00:20:00,670 --> 00:20:02,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Fans" like me...</font>

302
00:20:03,730 --> 00:20:06,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We don't accept things like that.</font>

303
00:20:12,670 --> 00:20:15,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I couldn't tell him 
that I'm his girlfriend.</i></font>

304
00:20:17,380 --> 00:20:18,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I need to go home.</i></font>

305
00:20:21,200 --> 00:20:23,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I wanted to see Kizuki.</i></font>

306
00:20:24,760 --> 00:20:26,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ouch.</font>

307
00:20:27,090 --> 00:20:31,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I shouldn't have worn my new shoes.</i></font>

308
00:20:32,460 --> 00:20:33,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoa!</font>

309
00:20:35,340 --> 00:20:37,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I rushed out and bought some chocolates.</i></font>

310
00:20:37,630 --> 00:20:39,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Acting like a girlfriend 
all of a sudden...</i></font>

311
00:20:43,530 --> 00:20:45,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I feel so stupid.</i></font>

312
00:20:46,650 --> 00:20:48,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm going nowhere, all alone...</i></font>

313
00:20:52,360 --> 00:20:53,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Found you.</font>

314
00:20:57,490 --> 00:20:58,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kizuki!</font>

315
00:21:01,170 --> 00:21:04,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you doing? 
Coming out here all on your own?</font>

316
00:21:05,450 --> 00:21:06,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh...</font>

317
00:21:06,420 --> 00:21:09,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This is the first time I've seen him 
make such a scary expression.</i></font>

318
00:21:10,170 --> 00:21:11,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What do I do?</i></font>

319
00:21:11,480 --> 00:21:13,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I made him upset.</i></font>

320
00:21:14,510 --> 00:21:15,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry.</font>

321
00:21:15,800 --> 00:21:17,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just wanted to see you, Kizuki.</font>

322
00:21:19,080 --> 00:21:21,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was going to leave 
as soon as I gave you this.</font>

323
00:21:23,410 --> 00:21:25,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry for being such an inconvenience...</font>

324
00:21:25,750 --> 00:21:27,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't do things like this!</font>

325
00:21:29,150 --> 00:21:32,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I heard from Coach 
that a girl came to visit.</font>

326
00:21:32,080 --> 00:21:36,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I immediately thought 
it was you, so I rushed over.</font>

327
00:21:37,570 --> 00:21:41,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was so worried you'd get lost.</font>

328
00:21:41,610 --> 00:21:43,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You wouldn't even answer your phone.</font>

329
00:21:45,070 --> 00:21:46,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't worry me like that!</font>

330
00:21:53,850 --> 00:21:56,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're loved by the person you love.</font>

331
00:21:56,980 --> 00:21:59,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're in the best possible reality.</font>

332
00:22:00,790 --> 00:22:03,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I... If something 
happened to you, Mizuho...</font>

333
00:22:03,860 --> 00:22:05,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't know what I'd do...</font>

334
00:22:10,200 --> 00:22:11,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kizuki.</font>

335
00:22:11,980 --> 00:22:13,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm?</font>

336
00:22:13,730 --> 00:22:15,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to kiss you.</font>

337
00:22:18,720 --> 00:22:20,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I understand now.</i></font>

338
00:22:21,190 --> 00:22:25,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>To be a "girlfriend" is to be 
the person most precious to someone.</i></font>

339
00:22:27,730 --> 00:22:31,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kizuki. You smell like the pool.</font>

340
00:22:34,420 --> 00:22:38,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And that's a huge miracle.</i></font>

341
00:24:09,970 --> 00:24:14,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an9}<font size="14"><font face="Arial"><font color="#1b1e1a"># 17 Feelings That Won't Go Away</font></font></font></font>

